VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT ^#!\s*/(?:bin/|usr/bin/env\s+)(?:bash|sh)\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:set\s+-[euo]*e|set\s+-o\s+errexit
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects shell scripts that do not enable errexit or pipefail safety options.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Missing errexit or pipefail Options.
